'''''En'aid''''' was a [[Ferryboat liner]] that carried smugglers from the ''[[Dunari's Rest]]'' when the latter was attacked by Imperial forces. It made it to the hyperspace intact thanks to assistance from the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

